OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrewdog abandons real      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fliving wage for employees  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Craft beer giant Brewdog will no longer
OL,6, pay its employees the real living wage.
OL,8,FWorkers will receive the UK            
OL,9,Fgovernment's national minimum wage of  
OL,10,F#11.44 an hour from April - below the  
OL,11,F#12 cost of living-based rate.         
OL,13,FThe Aberdeenshire-based firm said the  
OL,14,Fmove was "necessary" as part of an     
OL,15,Feffort to return to profitability after
OL,16,Fmaking a #24m operating loss last year.
OL,18,FBut former staff have accused the      
OL,19,Fcompany of "abandoning its principles" 
OL,20,Fover the move.                         
